sentence: List all boardgames by GMT.

sentence: Which organizations were founded in 1950?
sparqlQueGG: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Organisation { ?uri dbo:formationYear ?date } UNION { ?uri dbo:foundingYear ?date } UNION { ?uri dbp:foundation ?date } UNION { ?uri dbp:formation ?date } FILTER regex(?date, ^1950) }

sentence: Show me all museums in London.
sparqlQueGG: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Museum> ; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/location> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/London> }

sentence: Who is the tallest player of the Atlanta Falcons?

sentence: Give me all writers that won the Nobel Prize in literature.

sentence: Show me all basketball players that are higher than 2 meters.

sentence: Give me all Swiss non-profit organizations.
